Package de.matthiasfisch.mysticlight4j

Class LED

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.matthiasfisch.mysticlight4j.LED
  • public final class LED
extends java.lang.Object
    An LED of a Mystic Light device. This can either be a single physical LED or a group of physical LEDs such as an LED array on a mainboard.
